{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3394460/extras/gif_1.gif?t=1738346309\" /><strong>Shieven</strong> is a suspenseful exploration game that puts you in the shoes of an investigator whose financial situation is on the verge of collapse. In a desperate attempt to solve his problems, he takes on a case at the mysterious Luminora Hospital, a place shrouded in dark and chilling rumors.<br><br>According to the stories, those who ventured beyond the hospital's surface levels have never been seen again.<br><br>Dive into the depths of Luminora Hospital and uncover <strong>what happened there</strong> in the past...<br>Discover chilling <strong>secrets</strong> that were never meant to see the light...<br>Escape from <strong>terrifying creatures</strong> or monsters lurking below...<br>Pay attention to <strong><u>everything</u></strong>...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3394460/extras/gif_2.gif?t=1738346309\" />The <strong>Security Flashlight</strong> is a versatile tool designed to help you face any danger and explore new paths. You'll find it during your journey through the depths of the hospital. With its powerful light and sound, it becomes an indispensable ally to keep you safe and push forward in the darkest moments. <br><br>Use it wisely...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3394460/extras/gif_3.gif?t=1738346309\" /><strong>We</strong> are an indie studio at the beginning of our creative journey, focused on learning and improving continuously. Our plan includes releasing more chapters of <strong>Shieven</strong> and exploring new ideas, whether by staying within the same style or venturing into completely different genres. Additionally, we are <strong>open to collaborations</strong> to keep growing and deliver unique experiences 